        "title": "KeyPressed event in java",
        "body": "<p>I have just created a java tic-tac-toe game i would like to figure out how to run a method once the enter key is pressed during a certain condition an example is below...<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>if(/*condition is met*/){\n     //keyListener\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
