            "last_activity_date": 1351049213,
            "creation_date": 1351049213,
            "body": "<p>Caveat - It's been a while since I did desktop applications, but the java.awt.Component class has an addKeyListener() method which you can use to register a class that implements KeyListener - is this what you are looking for?<\/p>\n",
